Package: svn2rpm
Version: __VERSION__
Priority: optional
Section: web
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Schlomo Schapiro <svn2rpm@schlomo.schapiro.org>
Depends: rpm, subversion
Homepage: https://github.com/ImmobilienScout24/svn2rpm
Description: Create RPM package from SVN sources
 Export from SVN and build an SRC RPM package. Requirements:
  - SPEC file must be part of files checked out from SVN
  - VARIANT 1: SVN contains SPEC file and optionally SOURCES
  - VARIANT 2: SVN is exploded SOURCE0
